OL,3,CEvents to mark 25th anniversary of
OL,4,CLadbroke Grove rail disaster
OL,6,FMemorial events will be held on
OL,7,FSaturday to mark the 25th anniversary
OL,8,Fof the Ladbroke Grove rail disaster.
OL,10,FThirty-one people were killed and more
OL,11,Fthan 220 were injured when a rush-hour
OL,12,Ftrain collided almost head on with a
OL,13,Fhigh-speed train around two miles from
OL,14,FPaddington station, west London,
OL,15,Fshortly before 8.10am on October 5
OL,16,F1999.
OL,18,FIt was one of the most catastrophic
OL,19,Frail incidents in recent UK history.
