OL,3,CEvents to mark 25th anniversary of
OL,4,CLadbroke Grove rail disaster
OL,6,FA wreath-laying ceremony will take
OL,7,Fplace in a memorial garden near the
OL,8,Fcrash site at 8am, followed by a
OL,9,Fservice of remembrance at 11am at St
OL,10,FHelen's Church, North Kensington.
OL,12,FAround 250 people are expected to
OL,13,Fattend, including relatives of the
OL,14,Fvictims, survivors and representatives
OL,15,Ffrom the emergency services, local
OL,16,Fauthority and trade unions.
OL,18,FThe events will be led by the Rt Rev
OL,19,FDr Emma Ineson, Bishop of Kensington.
