OL,3,CEvents to mark 25th anniversary of
OL,4,CLadbroke Grove rail disaster
OL,6,FAn inquiry into the disaster revealed
OL,7,Fthat the Thames service travelling
OL,8,Ffrom Paddington to Bedwyn in Wiltshire
OL,9,Fhad gone through a red signal before
OL,10,Fcrashing into the London-bound high-
OL,11,Fspeed First Great Western train.
OL,13,FMark Phillips, chief executive of rail
OL,14,Findustry body the Rail Safety and
OL,15,FStandards Board, said: "The rail
OL,16,Findustry experienced one of its
OL,17,Fdarkest days at Ladbroke Grove 25
OL,18,Fyears ago.
