OL,3,CEvents to mark 25th anniversary of
OL,4,CLadbroke Grove rail disaster
OL,6,FThe general secretary of train
OL,7,Fdrivers' union Aslef, Mick Whelan, who
OL,8,Fis attending the memorial events,
OL,9,Fsaid: "As an industry we will never
OL,10,Fforget those who lost their lives,
OL,11,Fthose who were injured, and all those
OL,12,Ffamilies who were impacted and who
OL,13,Fsuffered because of the Ladbroke Grove
OL,14,Frail crash.
OL,16,F"And we should never forget the
OL,17,Flessons that we learned in what is,
OL,18,Fand what will always be, a safety-
OL,19,Fcritical industry."
