OL,4,CLadbroke Grove rail disaster
OL,6,FDangerous incidents of trains passing
OL,7,Fred signals have decreased since the
OL,8,Fintroduction of safety improvements
OL,9,Fsuch as the train protection and
OL,10,Fwarning system.
OL,12,FOffice of Rail and Road figures show
OL,13,Fthere were 287 signals passed at
OL,14,Fdangers ` when a train passes a stop
OL,15,Fsignal without permission ` on
OL,16,FBritain's railway in the year to the
OL,17,Fend of March.
OL,19,FThat is compared with 593 in 1999/2000.
